{
  "title": "ReFi Roundup #31: Extreme flooding and record heatwaves PLUS: ReFi 101, MRV 101",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-31",
  "html": "<p>Hello friends! <a href=\"https://about.me/Bati\">Bati</a> here, founder of <a href=\"neurinko.com\">Neurinko</a>, co-authoring this week's ReFi Roundup to give an update on our public goods stream to help small project developers leverage the power of digital MRV.</p><hr><h1 id=\"waking-up-to-climate-reality\">Waking up to climate reality</h1><p>People all around the world are waking up to the reality of our climate condition.</p><p>Scientists have been sounding the alarm for over 30 years, and unfortunately we are beginning to suffer from the devastating effects of inaction. </p><p>With <a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-62684037\">historic flooding in Pakistan</a>, <a href=\"https://www.newscientist.com/article/2334921-heatwave-in-china-is-the-most-severe-ever-recorded-in-the-world/\">record heatwaves in China</a> and skyrocketing energy prices in Europe‚Äîthere's never been a better time to dedicate your life to the climate symphony.</p><p>If you're already working in ReFi, let this be a resounding gong of encouragement to keep focused on making real-world impact. If you're looking from outside the Rabbit hole and feel moved to jump in‚Äîlook at ReFiJobs.com</p><h2 id=\"extreme-flooding-in-pakistan\">Extreme flooding in Pakistan</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">1,000 pakistanis dead<br>over 10 million (!) displaced <br><br>climate change causing extreme flood conditions  <a href=\"https://t.co/Mg7ktH0YzF\">pic.twitter.com/Mg7ktH0YzF</a></p>&mdash; ian bremmer (@ianbremmer) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ianbremmer/status/1563580127123890181?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 27, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"climate-crypto-and-mrv\">Climate, crypto, and MRV</h2><p>With the stakes of climate change accelerating before our eyes, it's encouraging to recognize that the solutions already exist. The problem is well defined.</p><p>The challenge is coordination. Decentralized finance and digital MRV (measurement, reporting and verification) are likely to be two game-changing tools in humanity's transition.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-amp-mrv-101\">ReFi &amp; MRV 101</h2></div><h2 id=\"refi-101-on-coincentral\">ReFi 101 on Coincentral</h2><p>With so much rapid innovation in the regenerative finance space, it can be incredibly hard to keep up and make sense of the market landscape as it evolves. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NiharNeelakanti\">Nihar</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ecosapiensxyz\">Ecosapiens</a> published a brilliant article covering over 140 organizations across the climate crypto space.</p><p>He dives into industrial economic theory and</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Co-founder and CEO of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ecosapiensxyz?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ecosapiensxyz</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NiharNeelakanti?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@NiharNeelakanti</a> breaks down how through crypto and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a>, we can drive the future of finance and ultimately reverse climate change!üå±<a href=\"https://t.co/HKEuy1BRqZ\">https://t.co/HKEuy1BRqZ</a></p>&mdash; CoinCentral (@realcoincentral) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/realcoincentral/status/1562457451894546432?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 24, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"circle-highlight-mrv101\">Circle Highlight: MRV101</h2><p>MRV101 is a founder's circle in the ReFi Summer cohort. It brings together eight founders who are driven to unlock measurement, reporting and verification (\"MRV\") in a decentralized way‚Äîspecifically for small project developers.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">This wonderful group of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Founders?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Founders</a> is collaborating in one of our <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FoundersCircles?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#FoundersCircles</a> behind the scenes to create public goods to help smaller scale projects understand and access MRV and dMRV.<br><br>Who should they talk to?<br>What resources are already out there? <a href=\"https://t.co/WpU5lP0kdk\">pic.twitter.com/WpU5lP0kdk</a></p>&mdash; ReFi DAO (@ReFiDAOist) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist/status/1556763765198258178?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 8, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n<figcaption>Anna Maria, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Adelessagh\">David Many</a>, Will Masters, Magenta Ceiba, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DarinaReFi\">Darina</a> Onoprienko, D Roland, Kennedy Nganga, Daryl Edwards</figcaption></figure><p>Traditional MRV approaches are costly, often constituting 30-40% of a credit sale. What's worse, these costs are even before any realization of revenues and therefore are only financially viable for large scale projects starting from 1200 hectares. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot-2022-08-28-at-21.33.15.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1082\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/08/Screenshot-2022-08-28-at-21.33.15.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/08/Screenshot-2022-08-28-at-21.33.15.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/08/Screenshot-2022-08-28-at-21.33.15.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot-2022-08-28-at-21.33.15.png 2174w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Given much of the world's food supply is produced by smallholder farmers, this is a significant opportunity for impact. smaller farmers especially need support in switching to regenerative practices to protect their farms and livelihood from the impact of climate change.</p><p>As GR15 approaches on 7 September, we are building a grant application for the <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/mcAzaR8r65\">MRV101</a> Circle to produce public good for the benefit of small scale regeneration projects!</p><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-events\">ReFi Events</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"online-and-in-person-events-to-get-your-refi-on-%F0%9F%94%A5\">Online and in-person events to get your ReFI on üî•</h3></div><h2 id=\"refi-lima-sep-2-%F0%9F%87%B5%F0%9F%87%AA\">ReFi Lima Sep 2! üáµüá™</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://dandelion.earth/events/62f9b15330d0ba0010ea8895\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/image-17.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1118\" height=\"636\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/08/image-17.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/08/image-17.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/image-17.png 1118w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><p>Our ReFi friends in Peru will be kicking off the first ReFi Spring event in Lima on September 2 at <a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/maps?q=UPC%20-%20Campus%20San%20Isidro,%20Avenida%20General%20Salaverry,%20San%20Isidro,%20Per%C3%BA\">Campus San Isidro, Avenida General Salaverry, San Isidro, Per√∫</a>. </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://dandelion.earth/events/62f9b15330d0ba0010ea8895\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Get tickets</a></div><h2 id=\"crypto-commons-gathering-2022-%F0%9F%8E%89\">Crypto Commons Gathering 2022 üéâ</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/image-15.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/08/image-15.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/08/image-15.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/08/image-15.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/image-15.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>After a successful gathering this spring, the folks from the Crypto Commons Association are back again! They kicked off a five-day event in a gorgeous setting of the alps with sponsorship from Regen Network, EthicHub, Block Science, Coordinape and Holochain.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/image-16.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/08/image-16.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/08/image-16.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/image-16.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-bites\">ReFi Bites</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"the-best-of-refi-twitter-and-beyond\">The best of ReFi Twitter and Beyond</h3><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/lists/1419697306887143431\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">Follow the ReFi List</a></div><h2 id=\"refi-podcast-follow-the-public-goods\"><strong>ReFi Podcast: Follow the public goods </strong></h2><p>If you haven't yet, join us in a conversation with Kevin Owocki, the co-founder of Gitcoin and Meme Lord at Green Pill book and podcast who has been pioneering impact hyperstructures to fund public goods and destroy moloch.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AQcFwFUw_7E?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Impact Hyperstructures with Kevin from Gitcoin | #refi #web3\"></iframe></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://pod.fo/e/139fe3\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Listen now</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Thanks for listening. <br><br>I wrote a bit about the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gitcoin</a> hyperstructure here but left out the bit about building/supporting other hyperstructures<a href=\"https://t.co/1FicQaRGEc\">https://t.co/1FicQaRGEc</a></p>&mdash; Œûwoki (ü§ñ,üíö) (@owocki) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki/status/1562274313641742336?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 24, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"this-week-in-climate\">This week in climate</h2><p>A great thread from our friend Nick at Keep Cool covers a bunch of major events in climate and climate tech this week, definitely worth a read. üßµü™°</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">2. China&#39;s historic heatwave üî•<br><br>The most severe heatwave &amp; drought on record in China is wreaking havoc on harvests, industry, &amp; is leading to increased coal use.<a href=\"https://t.co/qQoWRytqEL\">https://t.co/qQoWRytqEL</a></p>&mdash; nvo (@nickvanosdol) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nickvanosdol/status/1563938076669267968?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 28, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"staked-grants-coming-to-climate-collective\">Staked grants coming to Climate Collective</h2><p>A discussion on the Celo Forum posted by Helena Merk of Spirals Protocol. Now that <a href=\"https://medium.com/@ClimateCollective/introducing-the-climate-collectives-new-grants-program-2ec76b97318c\">Climate Collective Treasury</a> is now open for applications and 'wave 0' grants have already been approved, there's a solid trough of funding sitting around doing nothing.</p><p>Helena and Nirvaan opened a discussion around: \"staking a portion of already-committed grant funds (that would be disbursed after successful completion of a milestone) to the <a href=\"https://www.spirals.so/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Spirals</a> platform\" which would generate yield and provide financing for high-quality climate projects.</p><p>For those of you who don't yet know much about Spirals, \"Spirals redirects yield earned from staking CELO on a validator, to environmental assets from ReFi projects such as <a href=\"https://toucan.earth/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Toucan Protocol</a>\"</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://forum.celo.org/t/discussion-climate-collective-staked-grants/4170\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Discussion: Climate Collective ‚ÄúStaked Grants‚Äù</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Hi all, I‚Äôm pleased to share that the grants program supported by the Climate Collective Treasury is now open for applications! ‚ÄúWave 0‚Äù grant recipients will be introducing their projects and assets in this forum over the coming days, and we are thrilled to welcome them to the Celo community. Plea‚Ä¶</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard11/uploads/celo/optimized/1X/1e8f948f2419e94687fd6181495bf0686e267300_2_180x180.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Celo Forum</span><span class=\"kg-bookmark-publisher\">nirvaan</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard11/uploads/celo/original/1X/1e8f948f2419e94687fd6181495bf0686e267300.png\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><hr><h2 id=\"allcot-and-senken-march-together\">ALLCOT and senken march together!</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.allcot.com/\">ALLCOT</a>, one of the world's largest carbon project developers, and <a href=\"https://www.senken.io/\">Senken </a>have agreed to explore the regenerative climate finance ecosystem and on-chain carbon market technologies to develop more impactful climate projects.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/senken_io?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@senken_io</a> are thrilled to join forces with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ALLCOTGROUP?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ALLCOTGROUP</a> ‚Äî one of the world‚Äôs most established project developers üåè üå±<br><br>Why I am beyond excited for it üëá 1/7</p>&mdash; adrianxyz.eth (@mr_adrianxyz) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mr_adrianxyz/status/1562748238238625792?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 25, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"future-quest-premint\">Future Quest premint!</h2><p>on 19th August 2022, <a href=\"https://future.quest\">Future Quest</a> revealed the Mighty Dragon of Regen NFT, which drew a lot of attention and traffic to their <a href=\"https://discord.gg/WWpXpFmJjC\">discord server</a>! ¬†NFT project will offer community engagement and help accelerate their climate impact projects a.k.a. Quests. ¬†</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We have a date! And it&#39;s in the near future...<br><br>üíö September 9th 2022 üêâ <br><br>... It&#39;s not too late üëÄ<br><br>Signup: <a href=\"https://t.co/bMvPhTAh0x\">https://t.co/bMvPhTAh0x</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WAGFI?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#WAGFI</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Refi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Refi</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFTs?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NFTs</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Regen?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Regen</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreeMint?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#FreeMint</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/ZhUNlBDjK1\">pic.twitter.com/ZhUNlBDjK1</a></p>&mdash; Future Quest (@FutureQuestDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FutureQuestDAO/status/1562172874697441280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 23, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-medium kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-jobs\">ReFi Jobs</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"make-a-living-while-making-a-difference\">Make a living while making a difference!</h3><a href=\"https://Refijobs.com\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View Full Job Board</a></div><p>Right after the crypto market crash, many highly skilled professionals had to face lay-offs. I was one of them. Thankfully, ReFi Jobs was there to help me! check out the <a href=\"https://refijobs.com\">website</a> right away, if you're searching for a ReFi job!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/job/601233-founding-engineer-spirals\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123157_Chrome-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123157_Chrome-1.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123157_Chrome-1.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123157_Chrome-1.jpg 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123157_Chrome-1.jpg 2025w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/job/576207-senior-software-engineer-full-time-memexgarden\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123106_Chrome-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123106_Chrome-1.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123106_Chrome-1.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123106_Chrome-1.jpg 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123106_Chrome-1.jpg 2039w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://refijobs.com/job/595225-web3-content-and-community-specialist-greenclimatedao\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123228_Chrome-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123228_Chrome-1.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123228_Chrome-1.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123228_Chrome-1.jpg 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/08/Screenshot_20220826-123228_Chrome-1.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><hr><h2 id=\"other-refi-news\">Other ReFi news</h2><ul><li>Check out Aera Force's <a href=\"https://web3climate.substack.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Venturing in ReFi</a> for biweekly fundraising news and curated content for climate investors diving into web3.</li><li>Check out Toucan's <a href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/tag/decarbonized/\">deCarbonized</a> for bi-weekly tour through the carbon market space with a growing focus on removals.</li></ul><h2 id=\"final-thoughts\">Final thoughts</h2><p>During the opportunity presented to me, I wanted to highlight the work we're doing in the MRV101 Circle! I love interacting with pioneers who take actions and bring change! Thanking Djimo, Sev, David, Darina and Helena for their kind contributions in sharing their ideas for this newsletter.</p><p>Above all, I also want to thank John Ellison for providing me this opportunity. Finally, if you are also an innovator, feel free to get in touch and let's chat! As Timo from Basin DAO says, \"ReFi Spring is everlasting and let's continue our efforts to build a better future, together!\"</p>",
